divs: Sighting DetailsI was just looking at the stars with my Android sky map app and i noticed about 5 star like lights in a perfect angular formation traveling over me from south east to north west. It wasn't making any noise that I would have heard if it was a plane especially since it appeared to be flying closer to the ground then airplanes normally would. It looked also like a silhouette of a perhaps larger stealth structure in the form of a v shaped wing or some large wing typed craft.
